    "content": "<h4 id=\"prone\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; margin-bottom: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif; font-size: 0.35cm; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: #c40f0f; background-repeat: no-repeat; text-transform: uppercase;\">PRONE</h4>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 24px; color: #1c1c1c; font-family: 'Open Sans'; font-size: 13px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">A prone creature&rsquo;s only movement option is to crawl, unless it stands up and thereby ends the condition.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">The creature has disadvantage on melee attack rolls.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">The creature has disadvantage on ranged attack rolls against targets within 30 feet.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">An attack roll against the creature has advantage if the attacker is within 5 feet of the creature. Otherwise, the attack roll has disadvantage.</li>\n</ul>",
